    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine and transmission operate smoothly, providing a reliable driving experience. The interior is clean and smoke-free, though there is some light wear on the upholstery and floor mats. On the exterior, the paint still holds a nice shine, but you will find a few minor stone chips and a small scratch on the rear bumper. Overall, it is a dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
