      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "We are proud to present this meticulously preserved vehicle, currently maintained in showroom condition. This unit represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast, offering an uncompromising standard of excellence both mechanically and aesthetically. Every aspect of this vehicle has been curated to ensure it meets the most rigorous expectations of quality and performance. Experience the pinnacle of automotive integrity in a vehicle that presents as if it just left the assembly line.",
